item.title: Looking For A Somewhat Clean 562 Source + Client + Cache
item.dc:creator: @Tragedy1 Tragedy.
item.description:
@Tragedy1 wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:10, topic:528472”][quote author=Tragedy. link=topic=647225.msg4352663#msg4352663 date=1376943580]
The title really says it all, I want to start working on a new project and would really appreciate if anyone could get this for me.

Regards,
Tragedy
[/quote]
“Clean” means has the bare bones (It runs.).
“new project” means that you want something that you want to work on.
You just commented saying you want “100% combat and all skills” that is neither of the above.
Changing names, redoing shops, and stupid small things like that is NOT a project nor clean.[/quote]

I said SOMEWHAT clean. I’m not sure if you know what that word means, but the definition is:

To a moderate extent or by a moderate amount

Or, not completely. Just because I want combat added, doesn’t mean all I want to do is edit things. There is SO many more options in this brain of mine besides just ‘editing’ or ‘changing names’. Please, think about that
